author: The Irish Times
title: Coronavirus: Taoiseach details new restrictions
description: Everyone must stay at home in all circumstance, except for the following situations
content:
To travel to and from work for the purposes of work, only where the work is an essential health, social care, or other essential service that cannot be done from home (a list of these will be provided).
To shop for food or household goods, or collect a meal.… [+1589 chars]
